%#----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Setup
%#----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Prerequisites:

  * [Ruby] 1.8.6 or newer.

  * [RubyGems] 1.3.6 or newer.

Installing:

    gem install ember

Installing as a [Ruby on Rails] plugin:

    script/plugin install git://github.com/sunaku/ember.git

Upgrading:

    gem update ember

Removing:

    gem uninstall ember
